вҠў judge
  given summarizeвҶ’summary вүЎ "This code defines an event handling system. Key classes and functions: 1) EventBus вҖ” a class with methods __init__, on, use, and emit for managing event handlers. 2) TypedBus вҖ” a subclass of EventBus that adds schema validation. 3) create_saga вҖ” a function that takes a bus and steps, returning a run function that executes steps with rollback on failure."
  given criteriaвҶ’text вүЎ "The summary should identify architectural patterns, not just list functions. It should be useful to a new developer joining the project."
