  yield score вүЎ 4
  yield weaknesses вүЎ "1. No architectural patterns identified вҖ” the summary lists classes and methods but doesn't name the pub/sub pattern, middleware pipeline pattern, or saga/compensation pattern. 2. No explanation of relationships вҖ” how does TypedBus extend EventBus? Why does create_saga take a bus? 3. No mention of the middleware chain in emit() вҖ” this is a key architectural feature (interceptor pattern). 4. Not useful to a newcomer вҖ” they'd know WHAT exists but not WHY these abstractions were chosen or how data flows through them."

