--     (both: given sample-codeвҶ’code, yield summary)
--   вҠЁ В§summarize' вҲҙ block differs from В§summarize вҲҙ block вҶ’ вң“
--     (old: "Summarize this code file..." вҶ’ new: "Analyze for a new developer...")

