-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў improve
  given В§summarize вүЎ "вҠў summarize\n  given sample-codeвҶ’code\n  yield summary\n\n  вҲҙ Analyze В«sample-codeвҶ’codeВ» for a new developer...\n    Identify the architectural patterns...\n    Explain how classes relate...\n    Describe data flow...\n\n  вҠЁ ..."
  given judgeвҶ’weaknesses вүЎ "1. Doesn't explain WHY patterns were chosen... 2. Missing TypedBus-saga relationship... 3. No extension points..."
  yield В§summarize'

  вҲҙ Rewrite the вҲҙ block to fix the weaknesses. Keep given/yield/вҠЁ the same.

  yield В§summarize' вүЎ "вҠў summarize\n  given sample-codeвҶ’code\n  yield summary\n\n  вҲҙ Analyze В«sample-codeвҶ’codeВ» as an architectural briefing for a new team member.\n    For each component, explain: (a) what pattern it implements, (b) what problem\n    that pattern solves, (c) how it composes with the other components.\n    Identify extension points вҖ” where would a developer add new event types,\n    middleware, or saga steps? Describe the layering: base EventBus вҶ’ TypedBus\n    вҶ’ saga coordination.\n\n  вҠЁ summary identifies architectural patterns\n  вҠЁ summary is useful to a new developer"

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ В§summarize' has same given/yield signature вҶ’ вң“
--   вҠЁ В§summarize' вҲҙ block differs вҶ’ вң“

-- вҠўвҲҳ applies the rewrite: summarize replaced by summarize' for iteration 2.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- вҠўвҲҳ ITERATION 2 вҖ” improved prompt v2
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 8: summarize v2 (soft cell, LLM evaluation with twice-rewritten вҲҙ)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў summarize
  given sample-codeвҶ’code вүЎ "(full Python source)"
  yield summary

  вҲҙ Analyze В«sample-codeвҶ’codeВ» as an architectural briefing for a new team member.
    For each component, explain: (a) what pattern it implements, (b) what problem
    that pattern solves, (c) how it composes with the other components.
    Identify extension points вҖ” where would a developer add new event types,
    middleware, or saga steps? Describe the layering: base EventBus вҶ’ TypedBus
    вҶ’ saga coordination.

-- LLM evaluation:
-- The prompt now explicitly asks for pattern motivation, composition, extension
-- points, and layering. The LLM produces a comprehensive architectural briefing:

  yield summary вүЎ "ARCHITECTURAL BRIEFING вҖ” Event-Driven Module

LAYERED DESIGN: Three components stack from general to specific:

1. EventBus (pub/sub + middleware pipeline)
   PATTERN: Publish/subscribe with priority dispatch and middleware interception.
   PROBLEM SOLVED: Decouples event producers from consumers. Priority ordering
   lets critical handlers run first. Middleware enables cross-cutting concerns
   (logging, auth, rate-limiting) without modifying handlers.
   EXTENSION: Add handlers via on(). Add middleware via use(). Middleware can
   cancel events (ctx['cancelled']=True) вҖ” useful for validation or auth gates.

2. TypedBus extends EventBus (schema validation layer)
   PATTERN: Contract enforcement via schema registry.
   PROBLEM SOLVED: Prevents malformed payloads from reaching handlers. Fail-fast
   at emit() rather than debugging handler crashes.
   COMPOSITION: Inherits all EventBus behavior. Adds a pre-dispatch validation
   step via schema_registry.validate(). Transparent to handlers.
   EXTENSION: Register schemas per event type in schema_registry.

3. create_saga(bus, steps) (saga/compensation pattern)
   PATTERN: Saga with compensating transactions.
   PROBLEM SOLVED: Multi-step operations that need all-or-nothing semantics
   without distributed transactions. If step 3 fails, steps 2 and 1 are
   automatically rolled back in reverse order.
   COMPOSITION: Takes a bus parameter (can use EventBus or TypedBus). Steps
   are (action, compensate) pairs вҖ” the compensate function undoes the action.
   EXTENSION: Add steps as (step_fn, compensate_fn) tuples.

DATA FLOW: emit(event, payload) вҶ’ middleware chain (transform/cancel) вҶ’ schema
validation (TypedBus only) вҶ’ priority-sorted handlers вҶ’ results list."

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ summary identifies architectural patterns вҶ’ вң“ (pub/sub, middleware, saga, contract)
--   вҠЁ summary is useful to a new developer вҶ’ вң“ (pattern/problem/composition/extension)

-- Ready set after: { judge }

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- frame 9: judge v2 (soft cell, LLM evaluation)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў judge
  given summarizeвҶ’summary вүЎ "ARCHITECTURAL BRIEFING вҖ” Event-Driven Module\n\nLAYERED DESIGN: Three components stack...\n1. EventBus (pub/sub + middleware)...\n2. TypedBus (schema validation)...\n3. create_saga (saga/compensation)...\nDATA FLOW: emit вҶ’ middleware вҶ’ schema вҶ’ handlers вҶ’ results"
  given criteriaвҶ’text вүЎ "The summary should identify architectural patterns, not just list functions. It should be useful to a new developer joining the project."
  yield score, weaknesses

  вҲҙ Evaluate the summary against the criteria. Score 1-10.

  yield score вүЎ 8
  yield weaknesses вүЎ ""

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ score вҲҲ {1..10} вҶ’ вң“ (8)
--   вҠЁ weaknesses is empty iff score вүҘ 8 вҶ’ вң“ (score=8, weaknesses empty)

-- judgeвҶ’score(8) вүҘ 8 вҶ’ вҠўвҲҳ TERMINATES. Evolution complete.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- COMPLETE: 10 eval-one steps across 3 вҠўвҲҳ iterations
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
--
-- Iteration 0 (score 4): "Summarize and list functions" вҶ’ bare enumeration
-- Iteration 1 (score 6): "Identify patterns, relationships, data flow" вҶ’ names patterns
-- Iteration 2 (score 8): "Pattern + problem + composition + extension points" вҶ’ full briefing
--
-- The prompt evolved from 9 words to 54 words across 3 iterations.
-- Each rewrite was TARGETED: improve addressed specific judge weaknesses.
-- The interface (given/yield/вҠЁ) stayed frozen вҖ” only the вҲҙ changed.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- OBSERVATIONS
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= obs-evolution-works
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "вҠўвҲҳ EVOLUTION LOOP VALIDATES: the prompt improved from score 4 to 8 in 3 iterations. Each iteration: judge identifies weaknesses вҶ’ improve rewrites вҲҙ вҶ’ summarize re-executes. The feedback is SPECIFIC not generic вҖ” judge said 'no patterns identified' so improve added 'identify architectural patterns.' Judge said 'no extension points' so improve added 'identify extension points.' Targeted rewriting beats blind retry."

вҠў= obs-interface-freeze
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "INTERFACE FREEZE IS ESSENTIAL: across 3 iterations, summarize always had the same given (sample-codeвҶ’code) and yield (summary). Only the вҲҙ block changed. This is Liskov substitution for cells вҖ” any version of summarize is plug-compatible with judge. Without interface freeze, the вҠўвҲҳ loop would break the dependency graph. The constraint вҠЁ В§summarize' has same given/yield as В§summarize is not bureaucracy вҖ” it's structural integrity."

вҠў= obs-judge-improve-separation
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "SEPARATION OF JUDGE AND IMPROVE IS KEY: judge produces score + weaknesses. improve uses weaknesses to rewrite. They are different cells because they require different capabilities: judge needs EVALUATION skill (compare output to criteria), improve needs REWRITING skill (modify prompt to fix specific issues). Merging them into one cell would conflate analysis and action. Cell's dataflow makes the separation natural."

вҠў= obs-oracle-vs-evolution
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "ORACLES AND вҠўвҲҳ SERVE DIFFERENT PURPOSES: summarize has oracles (вҠЁ identifies patterns, вҠЁ useful to developer) that express the GOAL. The вҠўвҲҳ loop is the MECHANISM that achieves the goal. In iteration 0, oracles FAILED but we froze anyway вҖ” because вҠўвҲҳ handles retry through judge/improve, not through oracle вҠЁ? retry. This is important: oracle failure вү  cell failure when вҠўвҲҳ is driving. The oracles on summarize are aspirational constraints. The judge is the operational gate."

вҠў= obs-prompt-compression
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "PROMPT GREW FROM 9 TO 54 WORDS but could it shrink? The v2 prompt is verbose because each weakness got an explicit clause. A further evolution might compress: 'architectural briefing for new team member вҖ” pattern/problem/composition/extension for each component, with data flow and layering.' The вҠўвҲҳ loop found the RIGHT dimensions to include. A future crystallize step could distill the pattern: any summarization prompt needs {audience, structure, dimensions, flow}."

вҠў= obs-meta-pattern
  yield observation
  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "THIS IS THE META-PATTERN FOR CELL: write a soft cell with a bad вҲҙ, let вҠўвҲҳ evolve it until oracles pass, then optionally crystallize the final вҲҙ into a template. The human writes the WHAT (oracles). The machine discovers the HOW (вҲҙ evolution). This inverts traditional prompt engineering: instead of humans crafting prompts, humans craft evaluation criteria and let the system find the prompt. Oracles are the specification. вҠўвҲҳ is the compiler."
